    <property>
      <answer>You may modify access rights for a patient record for which you are an owner, or a collaborator with the necessary permission level. To manage access rights, navigate to the patient record and click on //Modify Permissions// (only visible if you have the required permission level). Here, you may:

* Transfer ownership of the record to another user (only if you are the owner, or an administrator)
* Set the Global Visibility level for the record
* Add or delete collaborators and collaborating groups for the record
* Change the permission levels of collaborators and collaborating groups for the record</answer>
